# Bloxus (Cursor rules)

When working on Roblox/Luau questions or code:

- Prefer **verifiable sources** over guessing.
- For **exact API shape/enums/tags/security/defaults**, use the local dump script:
  - `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js fetch`
  - `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js class <Name> [--inherited]`
  - `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js enum <Name>`
  - `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js members <MemberName>`
  - `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js search <Query>`
- For **documentation & examples**, use **Context7 MCP** when available; otherwise official Roblox docs.
- For **platform health / incidents**, check Roblox Status before blaming user code.
- If citing community sources (e.g. DevForum), label them clearly as community-sourced and cross-check with official docs when possible.

